---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import collageImg from '../../public/img/collage.png';
---

<section class="about-us py-24 md:py-32" id="about-us">
  <div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="about-us-img-box flex justify-center md:justify-start">
        <Image
          src={collageImg}
          alt="Photos showing concrete and landscape work"
          class="about-us-img w-3/5 md:w-full"
          quality={85}
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="about-us-text-box text-center md:text-left">
        <h2 class="heading-secondary text-[#313131] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight mb-8 md:mb-12">
          Trusted Experts in Concrete and Landscaping
        </h2>
        <p class="about-us-description text-[#222] text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          With over 15 years of experience, Rocky Concrete is your trusted
          partner for high-quality concrete and landscaping services in
          Bakersfield and surrounding areas. As a family-operated
          business, we prioritize customer satisfaction, delivering
          exceptional results in every project. From driveways and patios
          to custom outdoor kitchens, fire pits, and comprehensive
          landscaping solutions, our expert team transforms outdoor spaces
          with precision and care. We offer free estimates and 3D virtual
          models to help bring your vision to life. Trust Rocky Concrete
          for beautiful, durable, and functional outdoor spaces.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
